%90%E1%BB%91i-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i/poem-Y2dIt368yE6xrpoKgF03VA">Thủ 14 - Đối nguyệt thư hoài - 首１４</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-C%E1%BB%91c/Th%E1%BB%A5c-trung-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Oef8On7iKFCblvqq7-9Wtg">Thục trung kỳ 1 - 蜀中其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-C%E1%BB%91c/author-dSnmLveHQYvLVD8-n4k18A">Trịnh Cốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/U-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A2n-tu%E1%BA%BF-t%C3%A1c/poem-iYpPD6KWd8X-T-XaF9hWhw">U Châu tân tuế tác - 幽州新歲作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/author-AKTNQoEgmd-YADK1_8RKQg">Trương Duyệt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-Gia-To%E1%BA%A1i/X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-M%C3%B4n-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-c%E1%BB%B1u-t%C3%A1c/poem-sSOnvFtlBZJ-eo-5H0mLDg">Xương Môn phỏng cựu tác - 閶門訪舊作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-Gia-To%E1%BA%A1i/author-0o-a8tvzhzKvFpUKKgebkA">Trình Gia Toại</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
